          "caption": "Systems stories get more interesting when you can feel the pressure move through the stack.",
          "action": "add load",
          "idle": "system steady",
          "running": "pressure moving downstream...",
          "done": "6 infrastructure layers reacted"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "num": "02 · the move",
      "heading": "Version the things you can cache forever",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Static assets love long cache lifetimes when the filename changes with the content. User-specific pages need stricter rules.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "code",
          "file": "asset-name.txt",
          "code": "app.8f3a91.css\nkit.42aa10.js\n\n# new content, new filename, old cache stays safe",
          "caption": "Hashed filenames turn cache invalidation into deployment math."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "num": "03 · the check",
      "heading": "Inspect the headers",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">CDN bugs usually show up in headers: cache status, age, vary, and cache-control. Read those before blaming the app.</p>"
        },
        {
          "type": "lab",
