      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "The edge is part of the app",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">A CDN is not just hosting plumbing. It is where performance, correctness, and cache policy meet.</p>"
